itonic and\nphononic interactions in the CDW phase transition and the advantage of\ncombining complementary femtosecond techniques to understand the complex\ninteractions in quantum materials.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 11 Apr 2019 18:13:16 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 21 Aug 2019 12:51:20 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-09-30"}
