gorithm for finding a quasi-popular matching of\ncost at most that of a min-cost popular fractional matching is new; (ii) the\nproofs from Section 6.1 and Section 7.3 are now self-contained (the conference\nversion used constructions from [10] to show these lower bounds).\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 11 Apr 2019 22:33:03 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 17 Apr 2019 05:34:20 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Thu, 11 Jul 2019 00:01:33 GMT"},{"version":"v4","created":"Thu, 30 Jan 2020 19:29:59 GMT"},{"version":"v5","created":"Tue, 5 May 2020 04:08:40 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-05-06"}
