iable temperature window, by analysing\nthe finite-size data by XTRG simulations. For the QIM with a finite-temperature\nphase transition, we employ several thermal quantities, including the specific\nheat, Binder ratio, as well as the MPO entanglement to determine the critical\ntemperature $T_c$.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 12 Apr 2019 15:24:22 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-07-17"}
